  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I believe he was strongly anti-Nazi, and put the idea in our heads that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we got to watch it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Watch our step.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after the communist takeover, he became strongly anti-communist.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he died of a heart attack as a young man.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, every change, every political change brought its changes in its wake.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, of course, things changed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the same as the Nazis, it wasn't-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there wasn't a cutoff point.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Obviously, the communists came in to great influence with-- as the Russians came, as the Red Army occupied the country.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it took them several years to take over unlimited power.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Things were becoming worse all the time all along.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were tightening up the situation all the time, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nevertheless, it was livable until the Germans arrived in 1944.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- it was quite a reasonable life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I got to add the footnote there that people who were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] not born in Hungary or were not Hungarian citizens, they had an awful life even then.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were taken to the border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were literally chucked out of the country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on the other side of the border, as likely or not, the Germans murdered them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, look, anyone who-- whose grandparents were not born in Hungary, you had to be able to prove your-- your residency in Hungary to 1850.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so anyone who couldn't prove Hungarian citizenship was in big trouble.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the Jews who were Hungarian citizens, that lulled them into a false security saying that whatever happened to Jews in-- in Austria or in Poland, that can't happen to us because we fought for this country and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
